{
  "stem": "12612.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They never knew these things happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They knew from nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, how could they not know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With all the stench and all the stuff that's going on and the people talking in the towns, they had to know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Were they going to say, I knew, and I didn't do something about it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, they knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So the soldiers forced the little villagers to take us in and to feed us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were on a little chicken farm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the one soldier truck came with bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all of us, a lot of people, ran out to get the bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother sent me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I was a little shrimp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all these people were huge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all-- I was sticking my hand up to get the loaf.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all the other people were overhead grabbing for the bread.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember the soldier saying, this little girl was here first.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I took the bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went inside with that bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was-- in the beginning, not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They fed us baby food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then the soldiers said-- the American soldier said, you must eat a half a teaspoon of baby food at a time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We will feed you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You will get, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some people didn't listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they ate, and they ate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they gobbled everything up that they could get their hands on, a chocolate bar.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Whatever they found that the soldiers had, they wanted it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they didn't listen, and they died.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The-- the Russian soldiers also came to the little village, came to our house where we were staying and raped the grandmother and the mother and a 16-year-old girl.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The father was one of the Nazis in the War.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
